channel.title: Itemlist Error
channel.description:
I changed Black platelegs and Black Chainbody to Bandos Chestplate and Bandos Tassets, i compile i run and i get an error, i change back to normal, i compile run and this is the same error i get, it might not be because of the black, but i'm not sure :

item.description:
@CoonHunter wrote:

umm, did you just type that up? Or did you just Copy and Paste that, if you just copy and pasted it, then you have used spaces where tabs should be.

Also, the “item = 1077” peice, should not have the 2 spaces, but simply be “item=1077”.
